==English==
===Verb===
To kidnap [[Pacific]] [[Islander]]s or [[Kanaka]]s for work on, or for sale to, [[plantation]]s - usually [[sugar]] plantations in [[Queensland]], [[Australia]]. From [[blackbird]] - ref. to the colour of the people. 

Variant - (to) '''blackbird'''

===Derived terms===

===Noun===
'''blackbirder''' 
# a person involved in [[blackbirding]] (''plural'' blackbirders)
# a ship used for [[blackbirding]] (''plural'' blackbirders)

